<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8390547>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Chelicerae, ventral view. A–B. X. linzhiensis, female (A) and male (B); C–D. X. namchabarwa sp. n., female (C) and male (D); E. X. rigaze, male. F–H. X. shenxian sp. n., female (F–G) and male (H); I–J. X. benae sp. n., female (I) and male (J); K–L. X. xiangbi sp. n., female (K) and male (L); M–O. X. longlin sp. n., male (M–N) and female (O); Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8390547/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8390551>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. RTA, retrolateral view. A. X. linzhiensis; B. X. xiangbi sp. n.; C. X. namchabarwa sp. n.; D. X. shenxian sp. n.; E. X. longlin sp. n.; F. X. rigaze; G. X. benae sp. n.. Scale bars = 0.05 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8390551/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8390555>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Xizangiana linzhiensis. A–B. Female, habitus, in dorsal (A) and ventral (B) view; C–D. Male, habitus, in dorsal (C) and ventral (D) view; E. Female, metatarsus IV, preening brush, ventral view; F. Female, carapace, frontal view; G–H. Female, eye region, in frontal (G) and dorsal (H) view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8390555/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8390559>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Palp of Xizangiana linzhiensis, in prolateral (A), ventral (B) and retrolateral (C) view. D. RTA, retrolateral view; E–F. Expanded palp, in prolateral (E) and retrolateral (F) view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8390559/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8390561>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Female genitalia, in ventral (A, C) and dorsal (B, D) view. A–B. Xizangiana linzhiensis; C–D. X. namchabarwa sp. n.." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8390561/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8390575>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Xizangiana xiangbi sp. n.. A–B. Palp, in ventral (A) and retrolateral (B) view; C. RTA, retrolateral view; D–F. Bulb, in prolateral (D), ventral (E) and retrolateral (F) view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8390575/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8390612>
    dc:description "FIGURE 23. Records of Xizangiana species: 1 X. pawani comb. n.; 2 X. sedula comb. n.; 3 X. shenxian sp. n.; 4 X. rigaze; 5 X. benae sp. n.; 6 X. longlin sp. n.; 7 X. linzhiensis; 8 X. namchabarwa sp. n.. 9 X. xiangbi sp. n.." ;
